One-Year Senior Researcher Position in Homotopy Type Theory / Category =
Theory / Type Theory / Homotopy Theory
Carnegie Mellon University/Philosophy Department=20

The research group in Homotopy Type Theory at Carnegie Mellon University =
seeks a Senior Researcher or Visiting Professor (open rank), without =
teaching duties, for one academic year.  Suitable for a research or =
sabbatical leave from your home institution.  Position could begin as =
early as August 2017, or later.  Candidates should have a strong =
research background in relevant areas and a desire to collaborate with =
the existing research group, which consists of several faculty members, =
postdocs, and graduate students.

Questions about the position should be directed to Steve Awodey, =
awodey@cmu.edu.
Candidates should submit a CV and a brief research statement to =
CMUPhilosophy@andrew.cmu.edu.

